Description: S7 based framework for working with and standardizing neuropsychological test results. 
    Built in tools for working with the NACC Uniform Data Set (UDS) and the National Alzheimer's 
    Coordinating Center (NACC) neuropsychological battery, but with extensibility at the center of 
    the design.
